# Paper

This directory contains the manuscript and supplementary material associated with the MOSAIC molecular storage architecture.

## Files

- `MOSAICITMBMC.pdf`
  Main manuscript submitted to IEEE Transactions on Molecular, Biological, and Multi-Scale Communications (TMBMC).

- `SUPPLEMENTARY_MOSAIC.pdf`
  Supplementary material including additional figures, degradation experiments, convergence analysis, and extended recovery results.
